      "created": 1772463744,
      "updated": 1772463744
    },
    {
      "id": "68be3cf900000000001a3af9",
      "text": "[月食]",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1757297913,
      "updated": 1757301346
    },
    {
      "id": "68be65a10000000000c00a98",
      "text": "\t[2025/09/08]以来",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1757308322,
      "updated": 1757308328
    },
    {
      "id": "69a4c0220000000000d6d98b",
      "text": "\t雨だなぁ[inajob.icon]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772404771,
      "updated": 1772404776
    },
    {
      "id": "68be3d0100000000001a3afa",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1757297922,
      "updated": 1757297922
    },
    {
      "id": "69a599a4000000000057f141",
      "text": "[Mijikko.icon]",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1772460450,
      "updated": 1772460453
    },
    {
      "id": "69a599a7000000000057f144",
      "text": " ちょっとフライング",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1772460454,
      "updated": 1772460458
    },
    {
      "id": "69a599ac000000000057f145",
      "text": " [https://gyazo.com/3b98927d9c2a89e2b4f4e77942f0948d]",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1772460458,
      "updated": 1772460470
    },
    {
      "id": "69a599b8000000000057f146",
      "text": "  [J]だけ字体おかしくない？",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1772460470,
      "updated": 1772464303
    },
    {
      "id": "69a5a28300000000005842a0",
      "text": "   のび～してる[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1772462723,
      "updated": 1772462728
    },
    {
      "id": "69a599c2000000000057f147",
      "text": "  こういうフォントなの？",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1772460480,
      "updated": 1772460488
    },
    {
      "id": "69a59b220000000000fcb104",
      "text": "  [Open Sans] のようです。Cosense指定のUIフォントですね[Nrem.icon]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772460835,
      "updated": 1772460918
    },
    {
      "id": "69a59b400000000000fcb106",
      "text": "  [https://gyazo.com/61c429eaab455429de9f11e65f9ea4ff]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772460865,
      "updated": 1772460876
    },
    {
      "id": "69a59b320000000000fcb105",
      "text": "  https://fonts.google.com/specimen/Open+Sans?specimen.preview.text=Noto+CJK+JP",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1772460851,
      "updated": 1772460858
    },
    {
      "id": "69a5a68a000000000064d0fa",
      "text": "  　どうしてJだけこんな違和感が………[Mijikko.icon]",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1772463752,
      "updated": 1772463767
    },
    {
      "id": "69a5a891000000000027c1ef",
      "text": "  　じぇ～～～[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1772464273,
      "updated": 1772464283
    },
    {
      "id": "69a599a4000000000057f142",
      "text": "　もし仮に自分がSNS形式のツールを使って、自社向けに興味関心を伝えようとした場合のことを考えてみる",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1772460450,
      "updated": 1772464201
    },
    {
      "id": "69a5a84b000000000064d0fd",
      "text": "　　自分が発信する情報を極端に多くする例として",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1772464201,
      "updated": 1772464224
    },
    {
      "id": "69a5a863000000000064d0ff",
      "text": "　　　[チャットの投稿頻度を落とそうとする自分を見て、何してんだろうと思うことがある]にインスパイアされた",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1772464225,
      "updated": 1772464253
    },
    {
      "id": "69a5a85f000000000064d0fe",
      "text": "　　まあそもそも見ない人が殆どだと思う",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1772464221,
      "updated": 1772464270
    },
    {
      "id": "69a5a890000000000064d100",
      "text": "　　　個人が吐き出したものを大量供給しても価値はそこまで生まれないように感じる",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1772464270,
      "updated": 1772464316
    },
    {
      "id": "69a5a8c9000000000064d102",
      "text": "　　もしちゃんと見る人がいた場合",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1772464327,
      "updated": 1772464361
    },
    {
      "id": "69a5a8eb000000000064d103",
      "text": "　　　自身の[完璧主義]気質で[神経質]なのが災いして、見た人をもれなく[鬱]にしてしまいそう（",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1772464361,
      "updated": 1772464472
    },
    {
      "id": "69a5a905000000000064d104",
      "text": "　　　30回見たら心が死ぬSNS",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1772464387,
      "updated": 1772464404
    },
    {
      "id": "69a5a923000000000064d105",
      "text": "　　　何かと普通の人がスルーしてしまう細かい問題点を見つけてしまうことが多い",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1772464418,
      "updated": 1772464492
    },
    {
      "id": "69a5a960000000000064d106",
      "text": "　　　　神経質ってのもあるけど",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1772464479,
      "updated": 1772464525
    },
    {
      "id": "69a5a985000000000064d107",
      "text": "　　　　過程に対して深く理解しようとしたり、改善を試みようとしたりする癖もあって",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1772464515,
      "updated": 1772464661
    },
    {
      "id": "69a5aa17000000000064d108",
      "text": "　　　　というかそもそも面倒くさいの嫌なので、とにかく何か楽できないかで変なこと考えがち",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1772464661,
      "updated": 1772464685
    },
    {
      "id": "69a5aa34000000000064d109",
      "text": "　　　一度に直面できる問題の量には個人差が個人差があるので",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1772464691,
      "updated": 1772464721
    },
    {
      "id": "69a5aa58000000000064d10a",
      "text": "　　　問題をスルーすることで自我を保っている人には致命的だな",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1772464727,
      "updated": 1772464747
    },
    {
      "id": "69a5a8be000000000064d101",
      "text": "　最近のCosenseちょっと軽くなった？",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1772464317,
      "updated": 1772464331
    },
    {
      "id": "69a5a80a000000000064d0fc",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1772464136,
      "updated": 1772464136
    },
    {
      "id": "69a599a4000000000057f143",
      "text": "[mrsekut.icon]",
      "userId": "5b4ea932de544f0014198270",
      "created": 1772460450,
      "updated": 1772462263
    },
    {
      "id": "69a5a0b6000000000040ea21",
      "text": "\tCosense上にAI召喚させて会話できる仕組みを作ってみた",
      "userId": "5b4ea932de544f0014198270",
      "created": 1772462263,
      "updated": 1772462273
    },
    {
      "id": "69a5a0c1000000000040ea22",
      "text": "\t\t[https://gyazo.com/cf249c36a1b8bd01b87b10005453a639]",
      "userId": "5b4ea932de544f0014198270",
      "created": 1772462273,
      "updated": 1772462274
    },
    {
      "id": "69a5a0c2000000000040ea23",
      "text": "\t\t[/mrsekut-p/cosense-ai]",
      "userId": "5b4ea932de544f0014198270",
      "created": 1772462274,
      "updated": 1772462278
    },
    {
      "id": "69a5a0d7000000000040ea30",
      "text": "\t\tCosense上に任意の人格、任意の人数のAIを召喚できる",
      "userId": "5b4ea932de544f0014198270",
      "created": 1772462296,
      "updated": 1772462310
    },
    {
      "id": "69a5a0d4000000000040ea29",
      "text": "\t\tCosense上のボタンで起動・停止できる",
      "userId": "5b4ea932de544f0014198270",
      "created": 1772462292,
      "updated": 1772462310
    },
    {
      "id": "69a5a0d4000000000040ea2a",
      "text": "\t\t必要に応じて関連ページ先も見てくれる",
      "userId": "5b4ea932de544f0014198270",
      "created": 1772462292,
      "updated": 1772462318
    },
    {
      "id": "69a5a2ca00000000005842a1",
      "text": "\t\t[cosense-mcp-server]もそうだが、Cosenseにどう書き込むかのところで行き詰っているのでどう実装しているか知りたい[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1772462794,
      "updated": 1772462825
    },
    {
      "id": "69a5a2e900000000005842a2",
      "text": "\t\t 会話方法は[/mrsekut-p/cosense-conversation skill]を与えるだけで実現できるのか",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1772462825,
      "updated": 1772462900
    },
    {
      "id": "69a5a334000000000075f979",
      "text": "\t\t  去年は[Structured Outputs]で何とか表現できないか試してた覚えがあるが、そんなことせず[Agent Skills]を与えるだけでいけるんだ",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1772462900,
      "updated": 1772462966
    },
    {
      "id": "69a5a369000000000075f97a",
      "text": "\t\t  なんかすごい",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1772462953,
      "updated": 1772462957
    },
    {
      "id": "69a5a36d000000000075f97b",
      "text": "\t\t 書き込みはfunction callingみたいな仕組みかな",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1772462957,
      "updated": 1772462979
    },
    {
      "id": "69a5a383000000000075f97c",
      "text": "\t\t 　書き込み方式はinsert？patchで丸ごと書き換え？",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1772462979,
      "updated": 1772463006
    },
    {
      "id": "69a5a0d4000000000040ea2f",
      "text": "\t\t\t[@cosense/std]使って書き込んでるで！！誰が作ったんやろこれめっちゃ便利[mrsekut.icon]",
      "userId": "5b4ea932de544f0014198270",
      "created": 1772462292,
      "updated": 1772463327
    },
    {
      "id": "69a5a85a000000000027c1ea",
      "text": "\t\t\t すごい、一体誰が作ったんだろ[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1772464218,
      "updated": 1772465399
    },
    {
      "id": "69a5a9ea0000000000dcb2ac",
      "text": "\t\tすごい[yosider.icon]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1772464618,
      "updated": 1772464623
    },
    {
      "id": "69a5a93c0000000000dcb2a8",
      "text": "\t\t人間みたいに1文字ずつ書かせたい[yosider.icon]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1772464445,
      "updated": 1772464469
    },
    {
      "id": "69a5a99a0000000000dcb2aa",
      "text": "\t\t [ChatGPTの回答生成はStream派？]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1772464539,
      "updated": 1772464597
    },
    {
      "id": "69a5a9d30000000000dcb2ab",
      "text": "\t\t が、複数の書き込みが並列に起こる場合は面倒なのかな",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1772464596,
      "updated": 1772464596
    },
    {
      "id": "69a5a866000000000027c1eb",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1772464231,
      "updated": 1772464231
    },
    {
      "id": "69a5a866000000000027c1ec",
      "text": "[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1772464231,
      "updated": 1772464231
    },
    {
      "id": "69a5a867000000000027c1ed",
      "text": " [/hoshihara/合わせる顔がなくても会う]だいじ",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1772464231,
      "updated": 1772464237
    },
    {
      "id": "69a5a86d000000000027c1ee",
      "text": " 　[- 自分はできませんでした]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1772464238,
      "updated": 1772464244
    },
    {
      "id": "69a5a97a000000000027c1f0",
      "text": " [合わせる顔がない]とはちょっと違うが、明日先生と話をしに行くつもりだがあまり会いたくない",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1772464506,
      "updated": 1772465174
    },
    {
      "id": "69a5a9b7000000000027c1f1",
      "text": "  一難去ってまた一難というか、身から出た錆というか",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1772464567,
      "updated": 1772464576
    },
    {
      "id": "69a5a9c0000000000027c1f2",
      "text": "  正直もう限界",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1772464576,
      "updated": 1772464588
    },
    {
      "id": "69a5a9d5000000000027c1f3",
      "text": "  ゆっくり試験機直したい",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1772464597,
      "updated": 1772464605
    },
    {
      "id": "69a5aa91000000000027c1f4",
      "text": " 一旦寝よう",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1772464785,
      "updated": 1772464787
    },
    {
      "id": "69a5aa95000000000027c1f5",
      "text": "  ここ数か月ずっと睡眠リズムがめちゃくちゃ",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1772464789,
      "updated": 1772464802
    },
    {
      "id": "69a5ac490000000000dcb2ad",
      "text": "  良い選択だ[yosider.icon]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1772465225,
      "updated": 1772465286
    },
    {
      "id": "69a5a0b6000000000040ea20",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b4ea932de544f0014198270",
      "created": 1772462263,
      "updated": 1772462263
    },
    {
      "id": "69a5a6827838e300000075c32e",
      "text": "[2026/03/02]←2026/03/03→[2026/03/04]",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1772463744,
      "updated": 1772463744
    },
    {
      "id": "69a5a6827838e3000000cb4cbc",
      "text": "[/ [2026/03.icon]]",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1772463744,
      "updated": 1772463744
    }
  ]
}